16:39.503 --> 16:41.127
"Beam me... Beam me down, Scotty."

16:42.837 --> 16:45.627
- Was "Reading Rainbow" guy in...
- Geordi La Forge.

16:45.628 --> 16:47.294
Remember, like, the banana clips?

16:47.295 --> 16:49.961
You know, the girls used to...
