16:49.962 --> 16:51.752
I was like, "Captain..."

16:51.753 --> 16:54.794
"...to the board." I'm such a nerd.

16:54.795 --> 16:57.169
- Yes. Yeah, I agree.
- I think that might be the big reason

16:57.170 --> 16:58.961
why no one married me
'til I was like 30.

16:58.962 --> 17:00.961
Oh...

