19:38.170 --> 19:40.294
- Were you nervous at all?
- Yeah, just a little bit.

19:40.295 --> 19:42.169
It just showed
a little bit in the pitch.

19:42.170 --> 19:43.794
We can't see you, so all we're doing

19:43.795 --> 19:45.461
