23:11.212 --> 23:13.336
- ♪ Got no trouble today ♪
- Ah! No block.

23:13.337 --> 23:15.711
No block!

23:15.712 --> 23:17.794
- Yeah!
- That was awesome!

23:17.795 --> 23:20.377
- ♪ Oh, heavenly day ♪
- Go, Molly!

23:20.378 --> 23:27.502
♪ Heavenly day, heavenly day ♪

23:27.503 --> 23:35.669
♪ Tomorrow may rain with sorrow ♪

23:35.670 --> 23:42.544
♪ Here's a little time we can borrow ♪

23:42.545 --> 23:45.002
♪ I got nothing to tell you ♪

