♪ I got nothing much to say ♪

23:48.587 --> 23:52.336
♪ Only I'm glad to be here with you ♪

23:52.337 --> 23:57.377
♪ On this heavenly,
heavenly, heavenly, heavenly ♪

23:57.378 --> 24:02.544
♪ Heeaaavenly day ♪

24:02.545 --> 24:05.919
♪ Oh, heavenly day ♪

24:05.920 --> 24:07.544
♪ Heavenly day ♪

24:07.545 --> 24:09.544
♪ Heavenly day ♪

